

	 
       ~~~~~~~~   Blue Eyes   ~~~~~~~~      Crawl deep inside yourself  covered with your perfect hair  perfect Body  perfect life  and watch yourself fall to ruin  before your very Eyes.  everything that haunts you  you’ve brought with you here.  now your only Refuge  has become your greatest fear.  watch as your Shell crumbles  following the setting sun.  now the once safe Night  threatens to speak of what you’ve done.  don’t let your Eyes grow tired.  don’t let your smile grow thin.  know that you can always  Retreat farther within.  hold on to them for all you’re worth  try to save what’s left of your Lies  and keep trying to hide behind  your sad, vacant Blue Eyes.      ~fin~  
    
